<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Birthday Surprise</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:sans-serif;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd1dc,#fff5f8);
text-align:center;
overflow:hidden;
}

.page{
display:none;
height:100vh;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
flex-direction:column;
}

.active{
display:flex;
}

button{
padding:15px 30px;
font-size:18px;
border:none;
border-radius:20px;
background:#ff4f93;
color:white;
cursor:pointer;
margin-top:20px;
}

.nailong{
width:200px;
position:relative;
animation:walk 3s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes walk{
from{left:-100px;}
to{left:100px;}
}

h1{
color:#ff2f7a;
}

.slideshow{
width:250px;
height:250px;
border-radius:20px;
object-fit:cover;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<audio autoplay loop>
<source src="https://www.soundhelix.com/examples/mp3/SoundHelix-Song-2.mp3">
</audio>

<!-- PAGE 1 -->

<div id="p1" class="page active">

<img class="nailong" src="https://i.imgur.com/JqEuJ6t.png">

<h1>Hai kamu 👀</h1>
<p>Nailong datang bawa sesuatu...</p>

<button onclick="next('p2')">
Klik disini
</button>

</div>

<!-- PAGE 2 -->

<div id="p2" class="page">

<h1>🐉 Tebakan Nailong</h1>

<p>Hari ini ada orang spesial ulang tahun...</p>

<button onclick="next('p3')">
Siapa ya?
</button>

</div>

<!-- PAGE 3 COUNTDOWN -->

<div id="p3" class="page">

<h1>Tunggu sebentar ⏳</h1>

<h2 id="count">3</h2>

</div>

<!-- PAGE 4 BIRTHDAY -->

<div id="p4" class="page">

<h1>🎉 HAPPY BIRTHDAY 🎉</h1>

<p>Hari ini hari kamu!</p>

<button onclick="confetti();next('p5')">
Lanjut
</button>

</div>

<!-- PAGE 5 FOTO -->

<div id="p5" class="page">

<h1>Kenangan Kita 📸</h1>

<img id="slide" class="slideshow" src="foto1.jpg">

<button onclick="next('p6')">
Lanjut
</button>

</div>

<!-- PAGE 6 ROMANTIS -->

<div id="p6" class="page">

<h1>Untuk Kamu ❤️</h1>

<p>

Terima kasih sudah hadir di hidup aku.  
Kamu selalu berhasil bikin hari aku lebih bahagia.

Semoga di umur kamu yang baru  
semua impian kamu tercapai.

Aku harap kita bisa terus bersama  
dan membuat lebih banyak kenangan indah.

</p>

<h2>Happy Birthday Sayang 💕</h2>

</div>

<script>

function next(page){
document.querySelectorAll(".page").forEach(p=>p.classList.remove("active"));
document.getElementById(page).classList.add("active");
}

let count=3;

setInterval(()=>{
let c=document.getElementById("count");
if(c){
count--;
if(count<=0){
next("p4");
}
c.innerText=count;
}
},1000);

function confetti(){

for(let i=0;i<120;i++){

let conf=document.createElement("div");

conf.style.position="fixed";
conf.style.width="8px";
conf.style.height="8px";
conf.style.background="hsl("+Math.random()*360+"deg,100%,50%)";
conf.style.top="-10px";
conf.style.left=Math.random()*window.innerWidth+"px";

document.body.appendChild(conf);

let fall=setInterval(()=>{

conf.style.top=parseInt(conf.style.top)+6+"px";

if(parseInt(conf.style.top)>window.innerHeight){
conf.remove();
clearInterval(fall);
}

},20);

}

}

let photos=["foto1.jpg","foto2.jpg","foto3.jpg"];

let i=0;

setInterval(()=>{

let img=document.getElementById("slide");

if(img){

i++;

if(i>=photos.length){
i=0;
}

img.src=photos[i];

}

},2000);

</script>

</body>
</html>
